<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA18">
<l>koṇṭa tulakaṅ kuṟaḷuruvāyk kōḷariyā</l>
<l>yoṇṭiṟalōṉ mārvat tukirvaitta – tuṇṭatuvun</l>
<l>tāṉkaṭanta vēḻulakē tāmaraikkaṇ mālorunāḷ</l>
<l>vāṉkaṭantāṉ ceyta vaḻakku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That he took the world in the form of a dwarf, that, in the form of a murderous</l>
<l>lion, he put [his] nails in the chest of the bright forceful man, and that he ate</l>
<l>the seven worlds crossed by him [is good] conduct practiced by Māl with lotus eyes,</l> 
<l>the one who crossed the sky in one day.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
